  <section class="puremark-about">
    <div class="container">

      <div class="puremark-about-intro">
        <h2>Patented Growing Process</h2>

        <p>Each diamond is grown via the CVD process, but our CVD process is different – our diamonds are Single Growth As Grown. This process uniquely mimics how a diamond grows in the earth without interruption.</p>

        <p>The result is a diamond that grows free of visible growth lines with a bright, natural color without post-growth treatments. This single growth process, combined with superior cutting, is why your PureMark Diamond, powered by Clarity, is unparalleled.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="puremark-about-boxes">
        <h2>Why Choose PureMark?</h2>

        <div class="grid gap-lg">
          <a href="#superior-cut" class="col-6-sm">
            <img src="{{ 'inset-diamond-tweezers.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="" width="800" height="570" class="lazy">
            <h3>Superior Cut</h3>
            <p>See why our diamonds sparkle brighter</p>
          </a>

