            <div>
              <a href="#/" title="Close" class="modal-close">Close</a>
              <img src="{{ 'MJ-puremark-logo-tag.png' | asset_url }}" alt="" width="401" height="152" class="lazy modal-logo">
              <img src="{{ 'inset-diamond-tweezers.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="" width="800" height="570" class="lazy">
              <h3>Superior Cut</h3>
              <p>PureMark Diamonds feature superior diamond-cutting techniques. Visible in an asset
                device (we welcome you into our store to see it first hand), hearts and arrows are found in all our round lab-grown diamonds and premium cut fancy-shaped lab-grown diamonds. The result is guaranteed 3X (Excellent Cut, Polish, and Symmetry) quality on round lab-grown diamonds and VG+ (Very Good Plus) on all fancy-shaped lab-grown diamonds.</p>

                <p>All PureMark diamonds are cut with supreme precision, exhibiting exceptional beauty visible to the naked eye. They capture and reflect light in a way we haven't seen in lab-grown diamonds before, maximizing brilliance and fire and giving them the ultimate sparkle.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <a href="#absolute-origin" class="col-6-sm">
            <img src="{{ 'inset-ring-leaves.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="" width="800" height="570" class="lazy">
            <h3>Absolute Origin</h3>
            <p>Know your diamonds unique story</p>
          </a>

          <div id="absolute-origin" class="modal-window">
            <div>
              <a href="#/" title="Close" class="modal-close">Close</a>
              <img src="{{ 'MJ-puremark-logo-tag.png' | asset_url }}" alt="" width="401" height="152" class="lazy modal-logo">
              <img src="{{ 'inset-ring-leaves.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="" width="800" height="570" class="lazy">
              <h3>Absolute Origin</h3>
              <p>All Clarity Diamonds are “As Grown”. This means they have no post treatment to improve the color of the diamond.</p>

              <p>The standard CVD diamond is grown in multiple layers at the highest growth rate possible. The diamonds produced using this method often result in color grades that are subpar and require additional HPHT treatment to increase the color grades after the diamond is cut and polished. If diamonds are subjected to the HPHT treatment, the color can be improved up to three grades.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <a href="#gia-graded" class="col-6-sm">
            <img src="{{ 'inset-ring-rose.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="" width="800" height="570" class="lazy">
            <h3>GIA Graded</h3>
            <p>Assurance from a trusted source</p>
          </a>

          <div id="gia-graded" class="modal-window">
            <div>
              <a href="#/" title="Close" class="modal-close">Close</a>
              <img src="{{ 'MJ-puremark-logo-tag.png' | asset_url }}" alt="" width="401" height="152" class="lazy modal-logo">
              <img src="{{ 'inset-ring-rose.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="" width="800" height="570" class="lazy">
              <h3>GIA Graded</h3>
              <p>PureMark diamonds come with two reports: A GIA Diamond Grading Report - one of the premier credentials of a diamond's authenticity and quality and a GIA lab-grown report, or LGDR (Lab Grown Diamond Report), a new digital report of the 4Cs with a QR code link explaining the lab diamond's differences from natural diamonds. Each of our diamond's girdles is laser inscribed.</p>

              <p>We also offer the AGS Ideal® Report by GIA on all of our round lab-grown diamonds. It provides a light performance grade by analyzing its ability to absorb and return light (sparkle!).</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <a href="#as-grown-promise" class="col-6-sm">
            <img src="{{ 'inset-handshake.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="" width="800" height="570" class="lazy">
            <h3>As Grown Promise</h3>
            <p>Learn why not all diamonds are grown equal</p>
          </a>

          <div id="as-grown-promise" class="modal-window">
            <div>
              <a href="#/" title="Close" class="modal-close">Close</a>
              <img src="{{ 'MJ-puremark-logo-tag.png' | asset_url }}" alt="" width="401" height="152" class="lazy modal-logo">
              <img src="{{ 'inset-handshake.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="" width="800" height="570" class="lazy">
              <h3>As Grown Promise</h3>
              <p>All PureMark Diamonds, powered by Clarity, are “As Grown.” By growing our diamonds in a single stage, the end product is optically pure - there are no imperfections due to starting and stopping the process. This also means they have no post-growth treatment to improve the color of the diamond. Imitation being the highest form of flattery, we tip our hat to mother nature as we attempt to recreate her process.</p>

              <p>The standard CVD lab-grown diamond is grown in multiple stages at the highest growth rate possible. Diamonds manufactured using this method often produce subpar color grades and require additional HPHT treatment to increase the color grades. If diamonds are subjected to these HPHT treatments, the color can be improved up to three grades.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
